Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.41,0:00:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎 要打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.69,0:00:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我不會深入內部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且不事先確認Boss的模樣又怎麼能確立攻略方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.72,0:00:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold}閃爍魔眼

Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:08.70,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}認めてた臆病な過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:16.77,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}分からないままに怖がってた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:18.89,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}後ろの自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:25.72,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}現実を今に映す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:30.83,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}いくつもの空を描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:32.89,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}ここはきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:38.37,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}儚い心 乱して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:44.08,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}夢で高く飛んだ躰は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:46.94,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}どんな不安纏っても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:48.98,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}振り払ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:53.42,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}眠る小さな想い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:55.64,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}広がりだして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:57.70,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}気づく 弱い 私
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:04.40,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}君がいれば 暗い世界 強くいれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:10.16,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}長い夢見る心は そう 永遠で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:14.27,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:19.87,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I give you everything I have

Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:08.70,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}正視著膽怯的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:16.77,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}依然無法理解地畏懼著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:18.89,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}背後的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:25.72,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}此刻映照在現實中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:30.83,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}描繪了數片天空的此處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:32.89,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}一定是在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:38.37,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}亂我脆弱心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:44.08,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}乘著夢想高飛身軀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:46.94,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}無論有任何不安糾纏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:48.98,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}都掙脫前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:53.42,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}將沉睡著的小小的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:55.64,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}擴展開來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:57.70,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}意識到弱小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:04.40,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}只要有你在 黑暗的世界 也能一直堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:10.16,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}用沉眠許久的心 永遠堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:14.27,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:19.87,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I give you everything I have

