Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青眼之惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙看起來很棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乍看之下武器就只有大型劍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但應該還有特殊攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能把防禦力高的人集中到前線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後不斷進行切換了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:56.09,*Default,NTP,0220,0000,0000,,{\fs28}Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:02:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要有10個裝備盾的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你隱藏著什麼對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷不丁的說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說使用單手劍最大的優勢不就是可以持盾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我從來沒有看過桐人持盾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不持盾是因為這樣會降低細劍的攻擊速度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有以形象優先而不持盾的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委託莉茲打造的劍好像也沒在用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對技能刨根問底也不合禮數
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 雖然有點晚 我們來吃午餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你親手做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 記得摘下手套再吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這味道到底是怎麼做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我一年來的修行和鑽研的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我對艾恩葛朗特裡所能獲得的約一百種調味料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賦予味覺再生引擎的參數全部作出分析後做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是用格洛克瓦之種和修布爾之葉以及卡裡姆水製成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蛋黃醬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這是用亞皮魯巴豆和薩古葉和烏拉魚骨製成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這股讓人懷念的味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是醬油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三文治的醬汁就是用這個做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個賣出去一定能大賺一筆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還是不能賣出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:04:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的那份沒了就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是貪得無厭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心情好的話會再做給你吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 桐人 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還活著啊 克萊因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙還是那麼冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 身為獨行玩家的你怎麼會帶著女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我想大家在Boss戰的時候已經見過面了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過姑且還是介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是公會「風林山火」的克萊因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是血盟騎士團的亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 說句話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:05:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現延遲了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你好 我…我是克萊因 24歲 單身 現正招募戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是亞絲娜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都不是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且不論會長的長相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮尚往來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克萊因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我的長相怎麼了 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事啊 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我暫時會和這個人一起組隊 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先…先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是軍隊的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配著第一層的大型公會怎麼會派人到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從在攻略第25層時受到重創以後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起通關他們更側重於強化公會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都沒到過前線來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是隸屬艾恩葛朗特解放軍的柯巴茲中校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是桐人 獨行玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已攻略過前方的地帶了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 地圖完成至Boss房間前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我想請你把地圖檔案提供出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我們無償提供嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙知道完成地圖需要花多少心血嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:08:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將情報和資源都平等分給普通玩家並維持著秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時為了使所有玩家早日從這個世界中解放而戰鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 諸位協助我們是理所當然的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也打算回到城鎮後就公開這些數據
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你這也太好說話了吧 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有出售地圖檔案的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是想對付Boss的話 我勸你還是放棄比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這由我來判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我窺探了Boss的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是隨便湊幾個人就能敵得過的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的夥伴不都很疲憊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:09:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的部下們可不是因為這樣就示弱的懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們趕緊起立
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫人不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說 他們也不會魯莽地去挑戰Boss吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且去看看情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底誰才是老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然桐人不善言辭 不苟言笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個沉迷於戰鬥的大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這前面就只剩下Boss的房間了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定他們已經用道具回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快使用傳送水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 水晶使用不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明至今為止的Boss房間裡都沒有這種陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們解放軍中不存在撤退二字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥 繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡無法使用轉送水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們衝進去的話或許還能殺出一條退路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能做些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體 突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬著頭皮上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快退後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能使用那個了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 沒時間猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜 克萊因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 給我爭取10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切換
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星爆氣流斬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}Star Burst Stream
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼技能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束…了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人 快醒啊 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概昏迷了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就幾秒鐘時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 居然這麼亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再抱得這麼緊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的HP就要歸零了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯巴茲和另外兩個人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Boss攻略戰中出現犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自第六十七層以來第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種打法哪裡算是攻略啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯巴茲那蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都死了還有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你剛才用的那個到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非說不可說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種技能我從未見過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是「特殊技能」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:33.36,*Default,NTP,0095,0000,0000,,{\fs28}Extra Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二刀流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現條件是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的話我早就公開了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連情報商的技能列表裡也沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就說那是你專用的「獨特技能」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:48.20,*Default,NTP,0350,0000,0000,,{\fs28}Unique Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 桐人你太見外了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼厲害的殺手鑭居然一直秘而不宣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約半年前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我查看技能列表的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「二刀流」這個名字不知不覺就出現在那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold}二刀流\N能夠同時使用兩把劍進行攻擊的技能\N攻擊速度加成1.80\N武器防禦加成1.50\N冷卻時間加成1.20
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果被別人知道我擁有這種技能的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網絡遊戲的玩家都是妒忌心重的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣品格高尚的人就姑且不談
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們心生妒忌是在所難免的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是把辛勞視作修行的一環而好好堅努力吧 年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信口雌黃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去激活傳送門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了 交給你們好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經疲憊不堪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 回去的時候要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…桐人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子衝進去營救軍隊那群人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢 我真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已 再會了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還在想如果桐人死了的話我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最先衝進去的不正是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要向公會請假一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請假來做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.87,0:19:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前說過要跟桐人你組隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold}邀請\N收到來自Asuna的組隊邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,{\fad(400,0)\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold\bord0\shad2}2024年10月19日 第50層 阿爾蓋特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令軍隊的大部隊全軍覆沒的青眼惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被雙刀流使用者以五十連擊獨自擊破
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,添枝加葉也該有個限度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧這篇報導 一早就有一大群劍士和情報商蜂擁而至
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我有家歸不得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還不是你自作自受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟你把要求人家保密的事情給洩露出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦啊 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.14,0:21:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情變複雜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,{\fad(400,400)\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold\bord0\shad2}2024年10月19日 第55層 格朗薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還是第一次在Boss攻略戰以外的場合跟你見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 在之前六十七層的作戰會議上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾跟您交談過幾句
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希茲克利夫團長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是場艱苦的戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們公會也險些出現犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被稱作頂尖公會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰力卻一直很有限
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而你卻打算帶走我們公會裡十分重要的主力玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的重視她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就應該慎重地為她挑選護衛才對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對克拉帝爾一事給你們造成的麻煩深表歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就我們的立場而言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能欣然允許你把副團長帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想帶走亞絲娜的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用你的劍和你的「二刀流」來搶走她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能戰勝我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你盡可帶亞絲娜離開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一旦落敗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就必須加入血盟騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用劍說話 求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用決鬥來一決高下吧

Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:39.25,ED1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}遠くに聞こえた鐘の音が少し寂しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:51.29,ED1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}もう一度強く 今度は高く駆け抜けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:23:02.96,ED1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ただ繰り返す現実も 星の数の願い事も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.67,0:23:13.89,ED1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}目指すべき明日を見つけた この想いには勝てない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:24.78,ED1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}目の前に開かれた果てない世界 たとえ仮想でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:37.58,ED1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}迷い続けても 胸の奥で強くずっとずっと響いてく
